item.title: CVE-2018-17485|2024-09-17T02:05:43.929Z -- jolly%20technologies -- lobby%20track%20desktop
item.description: Lobby Track Desktop contains default administrative credentials. An attacker could exploit this vulnerability to gain full access to the application.

item.title: CVE-2018-17482|2024-09-17T03:49:17.112Z -- jolly%20technologies -- lobby%20track%20desktop
item.description: Lobby Track Desktop could allow a local attacker to obtain sensitive information, caused by an error in Reports while in kiosk mode. By visiting the kiosk and clicking on reports, an attacker could exploit this vulnerability to gain access to all visitor records and obtain sensitive information.
